---
import SecondaryLayout from "../../layouts/secondaryLayout.astro";
import "../../styles/components/horizontalCarouselManual.css";
---
<script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.13.0/dist/gsap.min.js"></script>
<script type="module" src="/scripts/components/horizontalCarouselManual.js"></script>

<SecondaryLayout title="Simple Carousel" rightLinkHref="">
    <div class="carousel-container">
        <div class="carousel-wrapper">
            <div class="carousel-track">
                <div class="carousel-slide">
                    <div class="slide-image">
                        <div class="blur-container"></div>
                        <img src="/assets/images/image-44.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide-description"><span>Every streak of light carries a story,</span> every blur a decision, every frame a reflection of what happens when instinct leads imagination.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-slide">
                    <div class="slide-image">
                        <div class="blur-container"></div>
                        <img src="/assets/images/image-13.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide-description"><span>Creativity moves through light,</span> reshaping whatâ€™s familiar into something alive, a blur of vision and instinct that refuses to stay still.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-slide">
                    <div class="slide-image">
                        <div class="blur-container"></div>
                        <img src="/assets/images/image-52.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide-description"><span>Each idea lives inside motion,</span> colliding with instinct, forming a rhythm that turns hesitation into confidence and every frame into imagination.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-slide">
                    <div class="slide-image">
                        <div class="blur-container"></div>
                        <img src="/assets/images/image-33.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide-description"><span>We design in motion,</span> guided by curiosity, chasing the line between control and freedom until thought becomes form and energy becomes expression.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-slide">
                    <div class="slide-image">
                        <div class="blur-container"></div>
                        <img src="/assets/images/image-20.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide-description"><span>Creativity is never still;</span> it thrives in velocity, where emotion meets precision and every blurred edge proves progress is always in motion.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-slide">
                    <div class="slide-image">
                        <div class="blur-container"></div>
                        <img src="/assets/images/image-19.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide-description"><span>From sound to texture,</span> from shadow to flash, creativity builds its own language, translating motion into an emotion that moves through every frame.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-slide">
                    <div class="slide-image">
                        <div class="blur-container"></div>
                        <img src="/assets/images/image-40.webp" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide-description"><span>In color we find clarity,</span> in motion we find truth, and in creativity we find the pulse that turns moments into something lasting.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="carousel-controls">
                <button class="carousel-button" id="previous" disabled>
